text: Bo Peep is a character of the Toy Story franchise, starting with Toy Story (1995). She is voiced by Annie Potts. ==Appearances== ===Movies=== * Toy Story (1995) * Toy Story 2 (1999) * Toy Story 3 (2010) * Toy Story 4 (2019) Category:Fictional characters introduced in 1995 Category:Kingdom Hearts characters Category:Toy Story characters
